root: ^This is my first time at the carnival.
^It's a little overwhelming but I think I'll like i here.
^I bet. Have you been on any of the rides?
^Rides? There are rides? This changes everything!
^Yeah, I keep looking at the roller coaster. I think I'll need to give it a ride...
^Well, I'm not waiting. I'll give it a go, too.
^If I can muster up the courage that is. I'm not as bold and brave as some of the other guests.
